ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:56:38.000Z","msg":"巴打 我唔係格硬罵戰<br />\n純粹個人意見  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1de77896d97d450290020e6d692cc3e735a5b6","tid":1418911,"uid":81071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e735706102f1ddc04bd3f161a0cba4acbe53f93","tid":1418911,"uid":161417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a0fdfc2d891132b9fb5299e7b4f69b9c20fac83","tid":1418911,"uid":161417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"df784acff3012c207291b9cb4cd0f5bd85ca3185","tid":1418911,"uid":81071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:51:49.000Z","msg":"都係果句<br />\n叫得港豬 吃喝玩樂就係佢地人生<br />\n佢哋一搬 骨子裡對中國都有小小抗拒<br />\n（可能會出入中國，但對如中國貨會抗拒，民權問題 都約莫知啲避而不談）<br />\n<br />\n但當影響交通 對佢地黎講就係人生大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仍然主張可免則免....."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:55:54.000Z","msg":"我反而主張不割就得<br />\n港豬習慣咗好快無野<br />\n只要你塞得夠多夠耐就得<br />\n好似十年前咁等一兩班地鐵就一定上到<br />\n後來三四班先上到 初頭仲有人屌鬼 宜家個個好習慣 包括我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:56:38.000Z","msg":"巴打 我唔係格硬罵戰<br />\n純粹個人意見  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:17:53.000Z","msg":"理解<br />\n其實唔係割唔割 問題<br />\n而係真心 見唔到政府高層官員 有咩影響<br />\n反而多左反抗爭者聲音<br />\n<br />\n我希望睇到多啲唔同意見 不論認同定唔認同<br />\n我同你可以有不同意見 自由表達<br />\n先係民主 自由精髓係未<br />\n<br />\n不割係當然的 但我更希望你嘗試說服我<br />\n<br />\n我當日先見過幾度有爭拗 <br />\n你話佢立場唔同都幫到口<br />\n但主要都係交通問題引起<br />\n我本身想幫忙 但我自己都唔知點幫<br />\n當然有人係咁講sorry<br />\n<br />\n我理解琴日有戰略必要<br />\n我亦唔希望講死話 一定唔可以<br />\n<br />\n我只希望日後前線可以 減少同避免 <br />\n始終 減少對平民影響 小個敵人都好"},{"pid":"5a274adcf07328700c15ac753fd055cf4bb540aa","tid":1418911,"uid":81071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:54:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4eb48206167fafc38ed1463b932702ad8ffcf33f","tid":1418911,"uid":165456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:55:47.000Z","msg":"勿忘初衷，輪到和理非出場喇"}]}